<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-mode</span>

(<span style="color:#008080">defhydra</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-hydra</span>
(<span style="color:#0086b3">:color</span> <span style="color:#008080">pink</span> <span style="color:#0086b3">:hint</span> <span style="color:#008080">nil</span> <span style="color:#0086b3">:post</span> (<span style="color:#008080">smerge-auto-leave</span>))
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;
</span><span style="color:#d14">^Move^ ^Keep^ ^Diff^ ^Other^
</span><span style="color:#d14">^^-----------^^-------------------^^---------------------^^-------
</span><span style="color:#d14">_n_ext _b_ase _&lt;_: upper/base _C_ombine
</span><span style="color:#d14">_p_rev _u_pper _=_: upper/lower _r_esolve
</span><span style="color:#d14">^^ _l_ower _&gt;_: base/lower _k_ill current
</span><span style="color:#d14">^^ _a_ll _R_efine
</span><span style="color:#d14">^^ _RET_: current _E_diff
</span><span style="color:#d14">&#34;</span>
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;n&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-next</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;p&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-prev</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;b&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-base</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;u&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-upper</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;l&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-lower</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;a&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-all</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;RET&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-current</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;\C-m&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-keep-current</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;&lt;&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-diff-base-upper</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;=&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-diff-upper-lower</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;&gt;&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-diff-base-lower</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;R&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-refine</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;E&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-ediff</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;C&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-combine-with-next</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;r&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-resolve</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;k&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">smerge-kill-current</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;ZZ&#34;</span> (<span style="color:#0086b3">lambda</span> ()
(<span style="color:#0086b3">interactive</span>)
(<span style="color:#008080">save-buffer</span>)
(<span style="color:#008080">bury-buffer</span>))
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;Save and bury buffer&#34;</span> <span style="color:#0086b3">:color</span> <span style="color:#008080">blue</span>)
(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;q&#34;</span> <span style="color:#008080">nil</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;cancel&#34;</span> <span style="color:#0086b3">:color</span> <span style="color:#008080">blue</span>)))
<span style="color:#0086b3">:hook</span> ((<span style="color:#008080">find-file</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">.</span> (<span style="color:#0086b3">lambda</span> ()

<h4 id="nyan-mode"><span class="section-num">1.16.9</span> Nyan-mode</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">nyan-mode</span>
<span style="color:#0086b3">:custom</span>
(<span style="color:#008080">nyan-cat-face-number</span> <span style="color:#099">4</span>)
(<span style="color:#008080">nyan-animate-nyancat</span> <span style="color:#008080">t</span>)
<span style="color:#0086b3">:hook</span>
(<span style="color:#008080">doom-modeline-mode</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">.</span> <span style="color:#008080">nyan-mode</span>))</code></pre></div>
<h4 id="hide-modeline"><span class="section-num">1.16.10</span> Hide Modeline</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">hide-mode-line</span>

((<span style="color:#008080">neotree-mode</span> <span style="color:#008080">imenu-list-minor-mode</span> <span style="color:#008080">minimap-mode</span>) <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">.</span> <span style="color:#008080">hide-mode-line-mode</span>))</code></pre></div>
<h4 id="line-number"><span class="section-num">1.16.11</span> Line number</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">display-line-numbers</span>

((<span style="color:#008080">prog-mode</span> <span style="color:#008080">yaml-mode</span> <span style="color:#008080">systemd-mode</span>) <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">.</span> <span style="color:#008080">display-line-numbers-mode</span>))</code></pre></div>
<h4 id="dimmer"><span class="section-num">1.16.12</span> Dimmer</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">dimmer</span>

<span style="color:#0086b3">:custom</span>
(<span style="color:#008080">dimmer-fraction</span> <span style="color:#099">0.5</span>)
(<span style="color:#008080">dimmer-exclusion-regexp-list</span>
<span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">&#39;</span>(<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*Minibuf.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*which-key.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*NeoTree.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*Messages.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*Async.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*Warnings.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*LV.*&#34;</span>
<span style="color:#d14">&#34;.*Ilist.*&#34;</span>))
<span style="color:#0086b3">:config</span>
(<span style="color:#008080">dimmer-mode</span> <span style="color:#008080">t</span>))</code></pre></div>
<h4 id="fill-column-indicator"><span class="section-num">1.16.13</span> fill-column-indicator</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">use-package</span> <span style="color:#008080">fill-column-indicator</span>

<h4 id="eshell"><span class="section-num">1.16.15</span> Eshell</h4>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-prompt-function</span>
(<span style="color:#0086b3">lambda</span> ()
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">format</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;%s %s\n%s%s%s &#34;</span>
(<span style="color:#008080">all-the-icons-octicon</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;repo&#34;</span>)
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">propertize</span> (<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">cdr</span> (<span style="color:#008080">shrink-path-prompt</span> <span style="color:#008080">default-directory</span>)) <span style="color:#990073">&#39;face</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">`</span>(<span style="color:#0086b3">:foreground</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;white&#34;</span>))
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">propertize</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;❯&#34;</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;face</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">`</span>(<span style="color:#0086b3">:foreground</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;#ff79c6&#34;</span>))
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">propertize</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;❯&#34;</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;face</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">`</span>(<span style="color:#0086b3">:foreground</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;#f1fa8c&#34;</span>))
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">propertize</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;❯&#34;</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;face</span> <span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">`</span>(<span style="color:#0086b3">:foreground</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;#50fa7b&#34;</span>)))))

(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-hist-ignoredups</span> <span style="color:#008080">t</span>)
(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-cmpl-cycle-completions</span> <span style="color:#008080">nil</span>)
(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-cmpl-ignore-case</span> <span style="color:#008080">t</span>)
(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-ask-to-save-history</span> (<span style="color:#0086b3">quote</span> <span style="color:#008080">always</span>))
(<span style="color:#0086b3">setq</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-prompt-regexp</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;❯❯❯ &#34;</span>)
(<span style="color:#008080">add-hook</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;eshell-mode-hook</span>
<span style="color:#000;font-weight:bold">&#39;</span>(<span style="color:#0086b3">lambda</span> ()
(<span style="color:#0086b3">progn</span>
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">define-key</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-mode-map</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;\C-a&#34;</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;eshell-bol</span>)
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">define-key</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-mode-map</span> <span style="color:#d14">&#34;\C-r&#34;</span> <span style="color:#990073">&#39;counsel-esh-history</span>)
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">define-key</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-mode-map</span> [<span style="color:#008080">up</span>] <span style="color:#990073">&#39;previous-line</span>)
(<span style="color:#900;font-weight:bold">define-key</span> <span style="color:#008080">eshell-mode-map</span> [<span style="color:#008080">down</span>] <span style="color:#990073">&#39;next-line</span>)
)))</code></pre></div>
